what_worked:
Applied decorrelate: ** Isolated date, item, and store filters into separate CTEs before joining with large fact tables. Materialized the month range calculation to decorrelate subqueries. Converted implicit joins to explicit JOIN syntax.

**Expected speedup:** 1.5-2x due to reduced join sizes from early filtering and elimination of correlated subqueries.
why_it_worked: Correlated subqueries re-execute per outer row; converting to JOIN eliminates per-row overhead
